    ExamTemplateQuestion --> QuestionType
    ExamTemplateQuestion --> QuestionDescription
    ExamTemplateQuestion --> Answer
    ExamTemplateQuestion --> Solution

    Solution --> SolutionDescription
    Solution --> SolutionWeight
